snippet.title: Doom 2: Ultimate Torment and Torture - 01 The Opening Abyss - All Secrets UHD 4K
snippet.description:
No commentary playthrough of the Doom addon Ultimate Torment and Tortute, showing all secrets.

UTNT is a compilation of all Torment and Torture levels published by Tormentor667 along with a bonus new Episode 4. UTNT was a showcase of GZDoom capabilities back in the day with lots of new enemies, weapons and massive Quake-ish levels.
------------
Playthrough sin comentar del addon para Doom "Ultimate Torment and Torture", mostrando todos los secretos.

UTNT es una recopilación de todos los mapas de la saga Torment and Torture publicados por Tormentor667, on un cuarto episodio extra. UTNT era toda una muestra de las posibilidades de GZDoom en su día, con cantidad de nuevos enemigos, armas, y enormes niveles con temática Quake.
